This paper deals with cross language text classification, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a novel multi-view learning method, which involves regularization and optimization techniques, making it relevant to categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with document representation and feature extraction, which are relevant to categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
